data.description: Spectacular Ranch on a quiet lot backing to woods! Bright and open floor plan with 3 beds, 3 baths, and over 1,700 square feet of living space, not including the finished lower level. Enter from the charming front porch where you are greeted by beautiful, newer laminate floors throughout. The expansive living room features a gas stove and access to the deck overlooking the peaceful backyard. Eat-in kitchen offers custom cabinetry, a large center island / breakfast bar, low-maintenance countertops, and breakfast room with built-in cabinetry and open views of the living room. Main floor also finds a formal dining room, a master suite, 2 additional bedrooms, and a 2nd full bath. The finished lower level includes garage access, a family/rec room, bonus room with kitchenette, a full bath, laundry, and additional storage space! Located in the Terre Du Lac lake community with convenient access to the lake, beach, sand volleyball, pickleball, clubhouse, and more!
